Show HN: Coclick.io – Build better demos with co-browsing
text:
Hi HN, I’m Philippe, cofounder of CoClick.

We believe that current video-conferencing tools are not suited for the sales process.

So we built a video-conferencing tool to help SaaS Startups, indie hackers and software developers build better demos.

The tech is already used by 10 clients we have in other industries, and we believe we can bring value to the tech industry.

Please do leave your comments below, we would love to hear your thoughts.
